        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Scientific Assistance for Very Endangered North Atlantic Right Whales Act of 2021 or the SAVE Right Whales Act of 2021</b></p> <p>This bill provides support for the conservation of North Atlantic right whales (<i>Eubalaena glacialis</i>).</p> <p>Specifically, it requires the National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration (NOAA) to provide financial assistance for the conservation of such whales.</p> <p>In addition, NOAA must conduct surveys of plankton on an ongoing basis using a continuous plankton recorder.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
